template: SELECT MIN(title.episode_nr) AS title_episode_nr, MIN(role_type.id) AS role_type_id FROM movie_companies, kind_type, company_name, role_type, cast_info, title WHERE cast_info.movie_id = title.id AND cast_info.role_id = role_type.id AND kind_type.id = title.kind_id AND movie_companies.movie_id = title.id AND company_name.id = movie_companies.company_id AND title.episode_nr < %s AND company_name.name LIKE %s AND cast_info.note IN ('(voice)', '(voice: Japanese version)', '(voice) (uncredited)', '(voice: English version)') AND title.episode_nr > %s AND title.production_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 2000 AND kind_type.kind IN ('movie', 'episode', 'series') AND cast_info.note LIKE %s;
